| Key | Action |
|--|--|
| `Shift+Right/Left` | move selection by one char |
| `Shift+Ctrl+Right/Left` | move selection by one word |
| `Shift+PgUp/PgDown` | move selection by one viewport |
| `Ctrl+A` | Select all |</markdown><markdown id="markdown10" x="777px" y="1436px" width="auto" height="auto" fontSize="16px">**Edit**

`Ctrl+E` opens file in editor of choice</markdown><markdown id="markdown11" x="124px" y="461px" width="auto" height="auto" fontSize="16px">**Go to line**

`Ctrl+G` opens input field for line number and scrolls to it
| Value | Action |
|--|--|
| N | Go to Nth line |
| +N | Go N lines forward (possibly EOF)|
| -N | Go N lines backward (possibly BOF) |</markdown><markdown id="markdown12" x="113px" y="909px" width="auto" height="auto" fontSize="16px">**Encodings**

